{"tid":88341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵食艱難】詐騙集團無底薪 3個月食白果得盒飯","createTime":"2017-01-20T14:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T14:16:55.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc780dd42fbc6ebb9e61ccedf1cb4bb049afd96","tid":88341,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170120&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56199819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170120%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56199819&d=QPwT%2ByELcvOQ3V%2B17dE42ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=da6ae95e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170120%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56199819&h=28d00b36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170120&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56199819</a><br />\n搵食艱難，肆虐兩岸三地的電話詐騙集團，原來也有辛酸。台灣一名男子租用新竹一處公寓作基地，找來7人打電話詐騙中國人，日前被警方查獲。他指，當日與上線約定抽詐騙所得3%當報酬，但3個多月都沒騙到人，沒拿到報酬。成員更向警方抱怨：「一毛錢都沒有，只有便當吃，實在做得很嘔。」"}]}